com.wikitude.tracker

Interface InstantTrackerListener


  • public interface InstantTrackerListener
    Defines all necessary callbacks for InstantTrackers

    • Method Detail

      • onStateChanged

        void onStateChanged(InstantTracker tracker,
                    InstantTrackingState state)
        Will be called when the state of the tracker was changed internally. It is called after a call to InstantTracker.setState(com.wikitude.tracker.InstantTrackingState)
        Parameters:
        tracker - The tracker whose state was changed internally
        state - The state to which the tracker changed

      • onStateChangeFailed

        void onStateChangeFailed(InstantTracker tracker,
                         InstantTrackingState failedState,
                         WikitudeError error)
        Will be called when changing the Instant Tracking state was not successful.
        Parameters:
        tracker - The tracker causing this error.
        failedState - The state that was not able to be set.

      • onInitializationPoseChanged

        void onInitializationPoseChanged(InstantTracker tracker,
                                 InitializationPose pose)
        Called repeatedly during the initialization phase with information about the tracking plane
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker who is being initialized
        pose - Information about the tracking plane

      • onTrackingStarted

        void onTrackingStarted(InstantTracker tracker,
                       InstantTarget target)
        Will be called when tracking is started. This is called first when switching from initialization phase to tracking phase, as well as later, when the tracking scene is recognized again after being lost.
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker that started tracking

      • onTracked

        void onTracked(InstantTracker tracker,
               InstantTarget target)
        Called repeatedly during the tracking phase.
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker that is tracking the scene
        target - The tracked instant target that contains information about the scene

      • onTrackingStopped

        void onTrackingStopped(InstantTracker tracker)
        Will be called when tracking of the scene is lost
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker that lost tracking of the scene

      • onPlaneRecognized

        void onPlaneRecognized(InstantTracker tracker,
                       Plane plane)
        Called whenever an instant tracker recognized a new plane that was previously unknown.
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker that recognized the plane.
        plane - The plane that was recognized.

      • onPlaneLost

        void onPlaneLost(InstantTracker tracker,
                 Plane plane)
        Called whenever a previously known plane is not found anymore.
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker that lost the plane.
        plane - The plane that was lost.

      • onPlaneTracked

        void onPlaneTracked(InstantTracker tracker,
                    Plane plane)
        Called whenever a previously known plane was tracked again.
        Parameters:
        tracker - The instant tracker that tracked the plane.
        plane - The plane that was tracked.
